        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1894893629" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18115048016781150810">I really enjoyed this read! I&apos;ve been wanting to read <i>Magnus Chase</i> for such a long time and I was definitely satisfied! <br/><br/>I really loved all of the characters, the world building, and all of the different adventures! I can&apos;t wait to read more of this series in the future.</span>
  <span id="freeText18115048016781150810" style="display:none">I really enjoyed this read! I've been wanting to read <i>Magnus Chase</i> for such a long time and I was definitely satisfied! <br /><br />I really loved all of the characters, the world building, and all of the different adventures! I can't wait to read more of this series in the future.</span>
